text: Kamyshtau () is a rural locality (a village) in Chukadybashevsky Selsoviet, Tuymazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 29 as of 2010. There are 2 streets.Карта Туймазинского района Башкортостана == Geography == It is located 48 km from Tuymazy, 11 km from Alexeyevka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tuymazinsky District
title: Kamyshtau
